{"tid":2182034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[庚子年]1840年係鴉片戰爭、1900年係八國聯軍、1960年係大躍進,2020年?","createTime":"2020-08-31T04:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:43:28.000Z","uid":267658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c3399e6bcbbacaa7f3af2231ceed2e489508c57","tid":2182034,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"今年2020年係60年一遇的「庚子年」<br />\n根據過往的歷史所得<br />\n每逢「庚子年」所發生的事件,係屬於「好大件事」和「影響深遠」<br />\n<br />\n睇番近代<br />\n1840年的「庚子年」,就爆發鴉片戰爭<br />\n1900年的「庚子年」,就爆發八國聯軍之役<br />\n1960年的「庚子年」,就爆發大躍進等大饑荒時期<br />\n<br />\n依三個歷史所造成的長遠影響,大家都知道<br />\n<br />\n而今年2020年的「庚子年」,已經過咗7個月<br />\n就已經發生咗好多影響深遠的事件<br />\n<br />\n再跟著剩餘的5個月?<br />\n會再發生什麼影響深遠的事件?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iIfqx2rsO14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiIfqx2rsO14&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr025ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=a15d9acc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iIfqx2rsO14</a>"},{"pid":"c3b90d6ccc5bfbf4eb795dd936e29dd49b63b421","tid":2182034,"uid":266428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"應該無野大得過中共武漢肺炎啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1d4b4621f2aa696456cbcbf1a9eba380139ce4","tid":2182034,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"呢啲巧合令嚟姐，唔通真係次次單數年 馬刺都拎總冠軍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470ae82e92dcaf8cae29c42f46f6884e7a4681a7","tid":2182034,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c1d4b4621f2aa696456cbcbf1a9eba380139ce4","tid":2182034,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"呢啲巧合令嚟姐，唔通真係次次單數年 馬刺都拎總冠軍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"但是,咁巧合就係今年大爆發得最勁"},{"pid":"04a1c2e42b313bc1b83328c82204f72832968c98","tid":2182034,"uid":67